<body>
    <h1>Steps to set up Cluster</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>To set up Cluster you'll need to:</p>
<ol>
<li><a href=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/Clustering#Clustering-DFSIOHandler">Set u=
p DFS Cluster</a> which moves binary files to NFS</li>
<li><a href=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/Repository#Repository-Persistencecachecon=
figuration">Configure Persistence Cache</a> to use Memcached or experimenta=
lly Redis</li>
<li><a href=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/HTTP+Cache#HTTPCache-UsingVarnish">Set up=
 Varnish</a>, disable Symfony HTTP Cache and set up cache invalidation to p=
urge Varnish cache</li>
<li><span class=3D"confluence-link"><a href=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/Sessions"=
>Configure sessions</a></span> to use a cluster safe sessions handling</li>
</ol>
<p>It is also highly recommended to set up <a href=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/So=
lr+Bundle">Solr Bundle</a>&nbsp;to be able to get better search, better que=
ry performance, be able to scale it, and offload database.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
